response.original_title: 郭富城 - 舞林密碼世界巡迴演唱會 香港站 2016 Aaron Kwok de Aa Kode - World Tour Live In Hong Kong 2016
response.overview: In late summer 2016, Aaron Kwok lit up the stage of the Hong Kong Coliseum with his de Aa Kode World Tour Live in Hong Kong. The Cantopop king kicked off the tour with 15 shows in Hong Kong, delivering dynamic and stunning performances of theme song "Dancing Fighter" as well as his all-time hits including "Wild City," "Give You Never Ending Love," "Password in The Wind," and "Love's Call."
